journal.title: Agropanorama : scientific and technical journal for the agro-industrial complex workers

person.name: Korolevich, N.G., Belarus State Agrarian Technical Univ., Minsk (Belarus)

abstract.value: It has been stressed in the article that it's essential to have a scheme of substitution for the analysis of dissymmetrical operating regime of transformers with the help of symmetrical components. The expressions have been received on the basis of which the schemes of substitution of the transformer Y/YhCY for currents of straight, reverse and zero succession are based.
